title: varieties
pid: d27fb486-cce4-47d3-8ac7-927434da9091
body: |2-
  - left : Preserve each ID from left, match it to IDs from right.
  - right : The opposite.
  - inner : Preserve only those IDs in both data sets.
            (Discards the most data.)
  - outer : Preserve all IDs.
            (Keeps the most data.)
  If both data sets have exactly the same IDs,
  all four become the same operation.
